Title: Fix missing navigation after automatic logout and login
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1614152128
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

When users were automatically logged out, for example due to inactivity, they
have to login again. After logging back in into the user interface, the
navigation was missing in some cases. We ensure now that the navigation is
visible to all users in such a situation.
